		<p>This sounds like a good idea to me! I end up writing a lot of howto documentation that assumes a fresh server, because that is what I am dealing with. A lot of the beginning steps are the same, and I&#8217;ve been think of modularizing them. I think a template system is the logical conclusion.</p>
<p>I like your format ideas, I hadn&#8217;t thought of stating how long each step should take. And being able to stop and come back is great.</p>
<p>Please update here with how this develops. I want to provide feedback and incorporate your template into my documentation. ^_^</p>

