<p>We&#8217;re dreaming that one day, we&#8217;ll generate the buildhelper UI straight from a text file with a special format. That way, you can keep it in a wiki, or a code repository, and we can refresh once a day with the latest updates.</p>
<p>(And for people who want to edit them on the web within the OpenHatch site, sure, we should support that too.)</p>
<p>I&#8217;m really excited about the &#8220;Click to get help&#8221; thing &#8212; it&#8217;s yet another way we can lure people into IRC who really should be there, but don&#8217;t know how useful a resource it is.</p>

